msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroZora_000"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah! Wandering around here and listening\n"
"to anecdotes about <2.se_co>Champion Mipha<3.re_co>\n"
"has truly invigorated me.\n"
"<4.an>In fact, it has inspired me to honor\n"
"her in my own way, separate from\n"
"my teacher's <5.se_co>unfinished song<6.re_co>.\n"
"<7.so>That is why I felt inclined to roost here,\n"
"near the <8.se_co>Divine Beast Vah Ruta<9.re_co>,\n"
"which <10.se_co>Mipha<11.re_co> herself mastered."
